data.title: Fred Astaire at AFI Life Achievement Awards
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.On April 17, 1984, Lillian Gish received the 12th AFI Life Achievement Award. Fred Astaire, seen here with wife Robyn Smith, hosted the televised tribute to Gish.
